{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"iAd Producer’s drag-and-drop interface makes it easy to lay out, customize, and test highly interactive iAd rich media ads. Discover how built-in page templates and components make ad creation a snap for designers without sacrificing the code editing and debugging capabilities that sophisticated developers expect. You’ll see how you can use iAd Producer to easily create complex ads, test your ad on your own iPhone or iPad, set breakpoints, step through code, and optimize performance."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/506\/"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC11","title":"Building iAd Rich Media Ads with iAd Producer","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-506-Building-iAd-Rich-Media-Ads-with-iAd-Producer"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-506-building-iad-rich-media-ads-with-iad-producer"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC11":{"url"